{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0002", "text": "大廈頂樓 定有階梯終於通得到", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 9, 0, 2, 5, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daai6", "haa6", "ding2", "lau4", "ding6", "jau5", "gaai1", "tai1", "zung1", "jyu1", "tung1", "dak1", "dou3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "大廈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "頂樓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "定", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "階梯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "終於", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "通", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得到", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0003", "text": "所以別說 高妹孤高總是追不到", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 5, 2, 4, 3, 2, 3, 3, 9, 2, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["so2", "ji5", "bit6", "syut3", "gou1", "mui6", "gu1", "gou1", "zung2", "si6", "zeoi1", "bat1", "dou3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "所以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高妹", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "孤高", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "總是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "追", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不到", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0004", "text": "害怕不自量力行過望見經已畏高", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 2, 0, 2, 0, 4, 2, 4, 3, 5, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["hoi6", "paa3", "bat1", "zi6", "loeng4", "lik6", "hang4", "gwo3", "mong6", "gin3", "ging1", "ji5", "wai3", "gou1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "害怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不自量力", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "行過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "望見", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "經已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "畏高", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0005", "text": "你沒有六尺高 你答應待我好", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 5, 2, 4, 3, 5, 4, 2, 5, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "mut6", "jau5", "luk6", "cek3", "gou1", "nei5", "daap3", "doi6", "ngo5", "hou2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "六尺", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "答應", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "待", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0006", "text": "努力也能彌補那點高度", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 5, 0, 0, 9, 5, 9, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nou5", "lik6", "jaa5", "nang4", "nei4", "bou2", "naa5", "dim2", "gou1", "dou6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "努力", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "彌補", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那點", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高度", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0007", "text": "對你印象還好 只不過自信差兩毫", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 5, 4, 2, 0, 9, 9, 3, 4, 2, 4, 3, 5, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["deoi3", "nei5", "jan3", "zoeng6", "waan4", "hou2", "zi2", "bat1", "gwo3", "zi6", "seon3", "caa1", "loeng5", "hou4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "對", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "印象", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只不過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "自信", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "差", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "兩毫", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0008", "text": "要是你樂意做 怎會給那幾寸難到", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 2, 4, 2, 9, 3, 5, 9, 4, 0, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jiu3", "si6", "nei5", "lok6", "ji3", "zou6", "zam2", "kap1", "naa5", "gei2", "cyun3", "naan4", "dou3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "要是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "樂意", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幾寸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難到", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "高妹正傳", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1742", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc0Mg_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
